ARRAY (limitations)
1.array fixed size(not growable in nature)
2.can store same type of data(homogeneous data)
3.implementing array not used any underlying data structures (cant support ready made method)


Overcome : collection framework used

1.collections are growable in nature
2.Heterogeneous and homogeneous data
3.collections must have underlying data structure(ready made methods are available)


